						               													<description>&amp;#10;     Do you like collecting things?&amp;#10;     Do you ever beg your friends to give you things?&amp;#10;     Do you regularly borrow things and never return them?&amp;#10;     Have you considered stealing things you want?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If any or all these things are true, then THIS is the game for you!&amp;#10;In Beg, Borrow &amp;amp; Steal players collect sets of 3 identical cards by taking cards from other players or stealing them from the draw pile. The player with the most completed collections when the Steal pile runs out wins! Some people work hard to achieve success, but in this game, you have to Beg, Borrow, and Steal to succeed!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Both The Light Edition and the Dark Edition can be played separately or together as an expanded version of the game. Each game is perfect for 3-4 players in normal play mode. When combined the game can accommodate up to 8 players in normal play mode or 3-6 players in challenging mode.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
